          "date": "2016-12-24 09:57:22.000000000",
          "tz": 330
        },
        "subject": "LU-8712 tests: refresh mgs config database before add mds",
        "message": "LU-8712 tests: refresh mgs config database before add mds\n\nconf-sanity test 72 failed to start mds because mds failed\nwith -EADDRINUSE. Registering mdt to MGS while mounting mds\nindex of mdt was already present in MGS configuration\ndatabase so mds mount failed with -EADDRINUSE\n\nFix:\nstop and format mgs when mgs and mds is separate. This will\nmake sure index of mdt will not be present in MGS config\ndatabase.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jadhav Vikram <jadhav.vikram@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: Idb317b4c57a902efb269afae968048367b656d1b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
